import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes as Routepage } from "react-router-dom"
import Login from "../components/login"

const Routes = () => {
    return(
        <>
            <Router>
                <Routepage>
                    <Route exact path="/" element={<Login />} />
                </Routepage>
            </Router>
        </>
    )
}
export default Routes
